These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-1::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, fonseca, davidoff
The people use 3 different means of transport: snowmobile, subway, taxi
1. the game-smoker is the person driving the subway##1
2. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
3. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the fonseca-smoker##3
4. the person driving the subway is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |
| Cigar   | game | davidoff | fonseca    |
| Transport     | subway    | taxi       | snowmobile |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-2::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  fisherman, librarian, pilot
House: farmhouse, colonial, townhouse
1. the farmhouse house is on the left of the colonial house##1
2. the pilot is on the left of the fisherman##1
3. the farmhouse house is on the far left or far right##3
4. the librarian is the townhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |     2     |     3      |
| Job     | pilot | fisherman | librarian  |
| House   | farmhouse  | colonial  | townhouse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-3::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, paramedic, videographer
There 3 different types of food: mango, radish, raspberry
1. the person eating radish is on the far left or far right##3
2. the accountant is on the far right##1
3. the paramedic is the person eating raspberry##1
4. the person eating radish is on the right of the person eating raspberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Job           | videographer | paramedic | accountant |
| Food   | mango        | raspberry    | radish        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-4::.
City: boston, prague, london
3 different pets are kept: fish, guinea-pig, mouse
1. the person traveling to london is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
2. the person traveling to london is on the left or right of the person traveling to prague##3
3. the owner of the fish is between the person traveling to london and the owner of the mouse##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| City   | london | prague | boston |
| Pet     | guinea-pig  | fish    | mouse  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-5::.
There are 3 different nationalities: indonesian, mexican, japanese
The people use 3 different means of transport: ship, subway, taxi
1. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the indonesian##3
2. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
3. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the indonesian##1
4. the indonesian is between the mexican and the person driving the taxi##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |
| Nationality   | mexican | indonesian | japanese |
| Transport     | subway   | ship   | taxi   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-6::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, chess, traveling
3 different games are played: scrabble, domino, backgammon
1. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
2. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
3. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is baking##3
4. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person playing domino##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |   2    |     3      |
| Hobby   | traveling | baking | chess      |
| Game     | domino  | backgammon | scrabble |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-7::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, rock, techno
There are 3 different favourite colors: mauve, white, ivory
1. the fan of techno is on the right of the person who likes white##1
2. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the fan of funk##1
3. the person who likes ivory is on the left or right of the fan of rock##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |     3      |
| Music-Genre   | rock  | techno    | funk       |
| Color   | white | ivory | mauve |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-8::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, milk
The people use 3 different means of transport: ship, taxi, van
1. the person drinking cola is the person driving the ship##1
2. the person driving the taxi is in the middle##1
3. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
4. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person driving the ship##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |   3    |
| Beverage   | milk        | fanta  | cola   |
| Transport       | van | taxi | ship |

