1. the fisherman is on the left or right of the nurse##3
2. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left of the teacher##1
3. the nurse is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2   |    3    |
| Job           | fisherman | nurse | teacher |
| Cigar   | dunhill    | bluemaster | vegafina     |

