.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-10::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, october, march
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: animation, musical, scientific
1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left or right of the person watching animation movies##3
2. the person watching scientific movies is on the far right##1
3. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3      |
| Birthday      | august | october    | march      |
| Movie-Genre   | musical       | animation | scientific |

