.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-11::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: basketball, badminton, skateboarding
The people have 3 different jobs:  dancer, photographer, security-guard
1. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
2. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the dancer##1
3. the security-guard is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
4. the photographer is on the left or right of the security-guard##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |      2       |       3        |
| Sport   | skateboarding | badminton         | basketball          |
| Job        | dancer | photographer | security-guard |

