.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-14::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, dancing, traveling
3 different pets are kept: rat, hedgehog, fish
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
2. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left or right of the owner of the fish##3
3. the owner of the fish is the owner of the fish##1
4. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |    3    |
| Hobby   | traveling    | baking   | dancing |
| Pet   | hedgehog | fish | rat |

