.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-20::.
House: palace, victorian, colonial
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: documentary, martial-arts, superhero
1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the colonial house##3
2. the victorian house is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
3. the palace house is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
4. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the victorian house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |      3      |
| House      | colonial    | victorian | palace         |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | martial-arts  | documentary |

 